Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:06.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the booster pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:09.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to check the tire pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:09.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:13.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll win today's race.\NIt's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and keep on working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:23.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hand me that cross wrench.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:36.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing the tires of the FD.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have a few sets in the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing the tires according\Nto the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:47.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready anytime, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:53.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Arigato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:57.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't it 10:00 yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:59.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still 9:40.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:13.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, that Eight-Six\Nhasn't showed up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:18.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure it would represent Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:21.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My prediction was wrong.\NIt's such a turn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:26.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I humiliate them by winning\Nthe time attack by a big margin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't ease my anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...what about the time attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna run for the Speedstars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji, you'd better prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're representing the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the starting point.\NAre you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:34.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the finish.\NEveryone's in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We can begin any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that.\NShall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So he didn't come after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:48.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:01.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.\NHow can you be my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji, you don't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:10.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sweating a lot.\NIt's painful looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!  Put your guts into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's begin the countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Hold a second!\NThis is the finish line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:29.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}A car just passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:34.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It could interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Should we wait until it reaches the peak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:41.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a public street.  There might\Nas well be oncoming traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:44.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.  Can you ask him what\Nkind of car it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell what kind of car it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:56.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...\NIt's got retractable lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's probably an Eight-Six Trueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What color was that Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Why're you asking me such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}White and black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}A panda Trueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?\NContinue counting down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:27.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop counting down, and wait\Nuntil the Eight-Six arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:32.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The One-Eighty beside me\Nisn't my true opponent.
Comment: 1,0:06:27.62,0:06:32.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0005,,\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji, you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are watery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:52.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man has come to save the\Npride of Akina's Road Racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:59.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if we win or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:19.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I feel awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}People are standing at every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:32.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've come to a strange place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:38.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...if I win, the tank will be full, and I can\Ngo to the beach without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:03.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The rear of the car, just leaving\Nthe corner, looked very steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:14.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like any other ordinary Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:20.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cars driven by those who can control\Ntheir car like their hands and legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...give off auras.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:26.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong aura surrounds Takahashi\NRyosuke's driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still weak for his brother, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:33.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But that Eight-Six had a strong aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:40.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's representing Akina, we can't\Npredict which one's gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:47.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Almost.  He's really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The fastest on Akina's downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}A legendary super technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:57.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}We can show the Takahashi brothers\Nthe true potential of Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Come on, Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:02.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm looking forward to seeing\Nwhat kind of driver he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I haven't felt such anticipation in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He put things off till the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But that trick won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Let me watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:17.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear the street!\NGuide it to the starting line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that car for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They were waiting for that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:41.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.  Where did all these people come from?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.04,0:09:59.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Fujiwara Tofu Shop (Private Vehicle)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that Eight-Six be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,T...that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NWhat happened to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because Dad told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:53.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the car's here, it won't do anything\Nunless your father is, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I shouldn't have come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That shitty old man pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:08.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, didn't your father say\Nanything besides that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:15.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad only told me to go to the mountain peak\Nand defeat the FD on Akina's downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:20.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father told you to drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...Takahashi Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't know unless I try...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I defeated him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeated him once...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:39.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll give me a full tank\Nof gas if I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you let me try, I'll win,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, excuse me, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, you complete moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:54.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:59.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, how can you be so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:03.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed just looking at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just move the car, and don't interfere\Nwith the time attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:14.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so dumb, and he doesn't\Nknow anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:25.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, your father isn't the only\None delivering tofu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You do too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:30.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,For the past five years,\NI've been the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,For the past five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get it, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you'll drive the time\Nattack on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...what're you saying, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:48.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If an amateur like Takumi pushes\Ntoo hard on Akina's downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'll lose control\Nand die instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, just go to\Nthe corner and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're here, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I'm tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takahashi Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make the same mistake twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:36.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A race between an Eight-Six\Nand an FD is so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:41.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Its power is totally outclassed, and the FD is\NJapan's best cornering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:45.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six is no match for it on\Nthe straightaways or corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:09.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...six...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...five...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...four...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...three...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:45.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Keisuke's FD is so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:49.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,350 horsepower isn't just for show,\Nand his clutch meet was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:50.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't be a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The full acceleration of the Eight-Six\Nalmost looked like it wasn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:06.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Judging from the start dash, that Eight-Six\Nhas 150 horsepower at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:09.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's far from the monster Keisuke says it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The reason why the shift timing is quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...is because it has a close transmission,\Njust like a rally car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:18.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That suits Akina's tight\Nhairpin curves perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:24.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Even so, I can't find any factor for that\NEight-Six to defeat Keisuke's FD.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:28.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The monster isn't the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Could it be the driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:44.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's not my style to go full out on the straightaway,\Nbut this is a time attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't see the Eight-Six in\Nmy rear view mirror again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That Eight-Six took an incredible line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It was 5 cm from the guardrail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}I've never seen any car\Nthat turns so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's gaining on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}His car is getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Something so absurd can't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A...are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:56.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi's father is a great Road Racer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen him a few times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like an ordinary tofu shop guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't judge a person by appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:10.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The manager told me that he's still\Nthe fastest on Akina's downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:16.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that old man sent\NTakumi here instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we have to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's much better than me driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:24.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how fast his\Ndad is, if it's Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:30.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it seems that Takumi has\Ndefeated Takahashi Keisuke once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:34.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi has defeated Takahashi Keisuke?!
